{"tid":440482,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"已經識用gimp，學校係都要用ps","createTime":"2017-10-18T22:33:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-25T03:48:47.000Z","uid":85946,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"f920a1b51a4249bd1f909d8b0f88c5dc3b0ba176","tid":440482,"uid":85946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T22:33:30.000Z","msg":"我今年年頭自學cut background png，<br />\n上網搵d免費software，費事又要破解又剩咁麻煩，就試下用gimp<br />\n<br />\n用左9個月左右，跟住今年開sem畫圖比同學以為我用小畫家畫圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  而家學校要我地學用ps<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  明明兩樣野都差唔多，我想知如果識用gimp，學ps上手會唔會快好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n求巴絲解答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad7c3a35be95343beaf4486a64cc048a31096ace","tid":440482,"uid":85946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T22:57:54.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a4ec5a8b0e78665479276367efa852cbdd02135","tid":440482,"uid":26675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T22:59:41.000Z","msg":"會<br />\n此post已完"},{"pid":"3d78da9be1928242b1084d442dd0d59681631c6e","tid":440482,"uid":85946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T23:09:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>會<br />\n此post已完</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我陣間翻去摸下先<br />\n<br />\n唔該哂巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f275c5586f5788136789383da90924e2d9f39f3","tid":440482,"uid":85946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T23:11:09.000Z","msg":"講普及度，如果ps係mac/window gimp係咪linux<img src=\"